               <msContents>
                  <summary>History of Ethiopia, by a Roman Catholic historian, in Amharic</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="4r" to="189r" facs="004">Fols 4r–189r</locus><title>History of Ethiopia</title><incipit xml:lang="am">መጽሐፈ፡ ምክር። በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ፩ አምላክ፡ አሜን፡ መጽሐፈ፡ ምክር፡ መዠመርያ፡ ክፍል፡። እግዜር፡ በቸርነቱ፡ ለባዊ፡ አድርጎ፡ ከፈጠረህ፡ ትውልድኽንና፡ ወገንኽን፡ ማወቅ፡ ይገባል<gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                  <textLang>Amharic</textLang>
                  <note>by a Roman Catholic historian, in Amharic. Organized into sections, e.g., Introduction (<locus target="#4r">fols. 4r, </locus>), How the Falasha came to Our Country (<locus target="#5v">5v, </locus>), About the Qǝmant Tribe (<locus target="#8r">8r, </locus>), About Muslims (<locus target="#9r">9r</locus>), etc.</note>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2"><locus from="192r" to="193r" facs="192">Fols 192r–193r</locus><title>Table of Contents</title>
                  <textLang>Amharic</textLang>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
